![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/78976b7e-5b77-483e-ac80-e1e156188b2f/Ep256.jpg)

What happens when one of the biggest baddies in the Marvel Comics universe sets his sights on Wakanda and its precious and rare vibranium? You get the Doom War story that sees Dr. Doom target T'Challa, Shuri and Wakanda itself in an effort to rob the country of the unique resource it's culture was based on. Join us as we review this comic, talk about the latest Wonder Man casting and speak a bit about Wakanda Forever before we review it next week!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
